title: Showerhead

claims.preamble: The ornamental design for a showerhead, as shown and described.

description: FIG. 1 is a perspective view of a showerhead of the new design;
FIG. 2 is a front elevational view of the showerhead of FIG. 1;
FIG. 3 is a rear elevational view of the showerhead of FIG. 1;
FIG. 4 is a left side elevational view of the showerhead of FIG. 1;
FIG. 5 is a right side elevational view of the showerhead of FIG. 1;

The portions of the Figures shown in broken lines are not part of the claimed design and are for illustration only.
